Dialogue: 100,0:00:03.60,0:00:05.04,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,În următoarea mea zi liberă?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:05.04,0:00:07.77,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Da, ai vrea să mergem undeva împreună?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:07.77,0:00:09.72,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Sigur. Chiar mi-ar plăcea!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:09.72,0:00:11.48,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Unde, totuși?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:11.48,0:00:12.65,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Oriunde dorești.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:12.65,0:00:14.76,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Te voi lăsa pe tine să alegi.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:14.76,0:00:15.87,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,În acest caz...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:15.87,0:00:17.88,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Mi-ar plăcea să vizitez orașul acestui castel!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:17.88,0:00:19.35,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Vreau să fac niște cumpărături
Dialogue: 100,0:00:19.35,0:00:22.50,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,și ar fi drăguț să am și niște timp să mă bucur de peisaje.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:22.50,0:00:23.95,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Bine. Așa rămâne, atunci.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:23.95,0:00:25.52,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Abia aștept!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:25.52,0:00:27.71,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Va fi atât de frumos alături de toți prietenii noștri!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:28.08,0:00:29.98,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Ei bine, mă gândeam că...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:32.84,0:00:34.30,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Am putea merge doar noi doi.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:37.49,0:00:38.68,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Bine!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:39.41,0:00:42.68,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,{\i1}O promisiune simplă îmi oferă atât de multă speranță.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:45.85,0:00:48.65,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,{\i1}Și, astfel, pot continua să înaintez fără ezitare.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:49.59,0:00:51.16,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,{\i1}Să continui să merg pe acest drum...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:52.98,0:00:54.91,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,{\i1}Și să-mi fac povestea să meargă spre zare.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:02.68,0:01:03.95,Dialogue,Garak,0,0,0,,Uimitor.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:04.45,0:01:07.35,Dialogue,Gaak,0,0,0,,Ai făcut toate astea de una singură, Shirayuki?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:07.35,0:01:08.00,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Da!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:08.00,0:01:11.38,Dialogue,WhatWasHisName,0,0,0,,Biroul botanistului șef e perfect curat.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:11.38,0:01:12.55,Dialogue,WhatWasHisName,0,0,0,,De câte ori pe an...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:12.55,0:01:15.43,Dialogue,WhatWasHisName,0,0,0,,Nu, de câte ori {\i1}viața{\i0} mea am văzut asta?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:18.64,0:01:21.02,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Doar am făcut curat peste tot.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:21.02,0:01:25.72,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Voiam să-mi iau liber mâine, deci am încercat să fac și treaba pe care aș fi avut-o mâine.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:25.72,0:01:27.97,Dialogue,Garak,0,0,0,,Oh, așa este, am vorbit despre asta.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:27.97,0:01:29.69,Dialogue,Garak,0,0,0,,Ai planuri mari pentru ziua de mâine?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:29.69,0:01:30.76,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Da!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:30.76,0:01:32.90,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Merg la cumpărături în oraș.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:32.90,0:01:34.02,Dialogue,Garak,0,0,0,,Înțeleg.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:34.02,0:01:36.99,Dialogue,Garak,0,0,0,,Nu ți-ai mai luat o zi liberă de ceva timp, deci mergi și distrează-te!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:37.48,0:01:38.31,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Așa voi face!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:39.25,0:01:40.49,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Voi pleca acum.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:44.48,0:01:47.08,Dialogue,Garak,0,0,0,,Ceva îmi spune că va face mai mult decât cumpărături.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:47.71,0:01:49.32,Dialogue,WhatWasHisName,0,0,0,,Chiar crezi asta?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:49.32,0:01:52.34,Dialogue,Garak,0,0,0,,Acel zâmbet timid, acei pași vioi și plini de entuziasm...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:53.06,0:01:55.96,Dialogue,Garak,0,0,0,,E clar ca lumina zilei pentru mine.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:57.17,0:02:00.14,Dialogue,Garak,0,0,0,,Merge acolo ca să se joace!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:01.18,0:02:02.19,Dialogue,Garak,0,0,0,,Știai?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:02.19,0:02:03.98,Dialogue,Garak,0,0,0,,S-a deschis un nou magazin în oraș.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:03.98,0:02:09.40,Dialogue,Garak,0,0,0,,Au mulți cățeluși pufoși cu care te poți juca în timp ce bei un ceai delicios!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:09.40,0:02:11.51,Dialogue,Garak,0,0,0,,Se vede că Shirayuki a făcut cercetări.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:11.51,0:02:14.16,Dialogue,Garak,0,0,0,,Știe ce e popular!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:14.16,0:02:15.16,Dialogue,WhatWasHisName,0,0,0,,Înțeleg!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:15.16,0:02:16.78,Dialogue,WhatWasHisName,0,0,0,,Ești foarte perspicace, herbalistule șef!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:18.15,0:02:20.13,Dialogue,Ryu,0,0,0,,Cumva, nu prea cred că e asta.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:53.40,0:03:56.25,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,După cum am spus, merg în oraș cu Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:56.73,0:03:57.93,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Doar voi doi?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:57.93,0:03:58.71,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:59.10,0:04:02.96,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,După problema de pe Insula Yuris, nu am mai avut timp liber deloc,
Dialogue: 100,0:04:02.96,0:04:05.30,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,dar acum se pare că putem să respirăm puțin, deci m-am hotărât să ies.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:05.63,0:04:10.48,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ai{\i0} fost ciudat de concentrat asupra treburilor tale în ultimul timp.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:10.48,0:04:12.70,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Voi fi plecat întreaga zi, nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:13.86,0:04:15.81,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Putem veni și eu, și Kiki?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:17.92,0:04:19.57,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Doar glumeam, mă jur.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:19.57,0:04:22.45,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Ei bine, banuiesc că {\i1}e{\i0} o întâlnire, la urma urmei.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:24.12,0:04:26.46,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,Știți, domnița mi-a spus și mie.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:26.46,0:04:30.07,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,A spus doar că merge cu tine în oraș,
Dialogue: 100,0:04:30.07,0:04:32.04,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,dar când te gândești că era, de fapt, o întâlnire...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:32.38,0:04:35.37,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Mi-aș dori să nu mai faci astfel de presupuneri!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:35.37,0:04:38.24,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,Știi, din cauză că ești așa înțepat
Dialogue: 100,0:04:38.24,0:04:42.84,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,nu i-ai spus încă domniței că e drăguță sau ceva asemănător.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:44.10,0:04:46.21,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Nu ai habar ce vorbești!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:46.21,0:04:48.75,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,Oh, se pare că am atins un punct sensibil.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:48.75,0:04:50.43,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,Mă gândeam eu.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:51.60,0:04:54.25,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,De ce nu-i spui câteva ceva drăguț din când în când?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:55.96,0:04:59.59,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,Cum ar fi: „Arăți foarte bine astăzi!” sau ceva asemănător.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:59.59,0:05:02.39,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,Pariez că asta e ceea ce crezi, dar nu o spui.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:02.39,0:05:03.15,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,De fapt, am făcut-o.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:03.78,0:05:05.67,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,I-am spus că arăta bine într-o haină.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:05.67,0:05:07.87,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,Oh? Când a fost asta?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:08.96,0:05:11.29,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,De Ziua Vizitării Castelului.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:11.96,0:05:14.66,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,În legătură cu agrafa de păr pe care i-ai dat-o.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:16.71,0:05:18.92,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Vrei să zbori cumva?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:19.34,0:05:21.11,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,În acest caz, arătați-mi voi cum se face!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:21.69,0:05:22.99,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Mai întâi, Mitsuhide!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:23.80,0:05:25.57,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Nu mă implica în asta!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:25.57,0:05:28.01,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,Haide, tânărul meu nobil, e momentul tău să strălucești!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:28.01,0:05:30.14,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,Imaginează-ți că domnița e în fața ta!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:30.43,0:05:31.76,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,Haide! Cucerește-o!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:38.54,0:05:41.61,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Shirayuki, ești mereu atât de calmă încât mi se pare drăguț!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:46.49,0:05:49.62,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Hei! Credeam că lucrăm împreună aici!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:53.17,0:05:54.73,Dialogue,Kiki,0,0,0,,Continuă, te rog.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:54.73,0:05:55.80,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Ei bine, vezi tu...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:55.80,0:05:58.50,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,My apologies if we were being too loud.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:10.18,0:06:11.68,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Sunt gata acum!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:14.30,0:06:15.50,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,Domniță.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:15.50,0:06:16.98,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,Ai terminat cu pregătirile?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:16.98,0:06:18.26,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Obi!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:18.26,0:06:21.15,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,Te voi conduce eu la el.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:22.70,0:06:24.15,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Voi lăsa restul în seama ta.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:24.15,0:06:25.25,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Bine.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:25.25,0:06:26.90,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Ai grijă, Zen.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:32.08,0:06:33.53,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Hei, Mitsuhide.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:33.85,0:06:35.01,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Da?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:35.01,0:06:36.37,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Ce e o întâlnire?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:37.62,0:06:39.69,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Am auzit soldații vorbind despre asta.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:39.69,0:06:41.12,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Deci ce e o întâlnire?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:42.00,0:06:44.43,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,E-Ei bine... Cum ar trebui să explic...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:44.43,0:06:49.61,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Bănuiesc că e atunci când mergi ieși undeva cu jumătatea ta.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:49.61,0:06:52.47,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Vă plimbați prin oraș, faceți cumpărături împreună...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:52.47,0:06:53.95,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Asta e tot?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:53.95,0:06:56.85,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Mâncați împreună, vă țineți de mână...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:56.85,0:06:58.00,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:58.00,0:07:00.17,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Înțeleg. Iar apoi vă sărutați, nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:00.17,0:07:02.23,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Dar tu probabil ai fii prea încordat ca să încerci!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:07.86,0:07:10.03,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Dar nici eu nu voi avea ocazia să fac așa ceva.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:10.81,0:07:13.13,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Nu e de mirare că nu am auzit de asta până acum.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:17.79,0:07:19.46,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Nu știi niciodată.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:20.11,0:07:22.71,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Poate va veni o zi când vei avea ocazia.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:25.69,0:07:27.17,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Continuă să visezi.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:27.67,0:07:29.29,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Timpul chiar zboară, nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:29.89,0:07:31.07,Dialogue,Kiki,0,0,0,,Ce s-a întâmplat?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:31.07,0:07:33.76,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Nimic, eram doar pierdut în amintiri.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:35.80,0:07:37.26,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Vremea chiar e plăcută astăzi.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:37.76,0:07:38.81,Dialogue,Kiki,0,0,0,,Așa e.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:43.71,0:07:46.02,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,Stăpânul ar trebui să vină curând, nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:46.41,0:07:48.60,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,D-Da.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:48.60,0:07:51.45,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,Domniță, nu-mi spune că ești agitată!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:51.45,0:07:53.67,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,De ce aș fi?!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:53.67,0:07:55.38,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,Nu pari să fii tu însăți astăzi.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:55.38,0:07:57.38,Dialogue,Ryu,0,0,0,,Ești încordată.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:57.38,0:07:59.12,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,S-Serios?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:59.99,0:08:04.87,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,O plimbare cu Zen ar trebui să fie ceva obișnuit. Nu m-am mai gândit la asta până acum.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:05.43,0:08:07.09,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Dar nu mă pot liniști astăzi.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:07.09,0:08:09.51,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,Dacă așa stă treaba, poate ar trebui să vin și eu cu voi.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:10.96,0:08:12.26,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,Glumesc!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:12.26,0:08:15.17,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,Dar trebuie să spun, nu mă așteptam să dăm peste Ryu!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:15.17,0:08:17.62,Dialogue,Ryu,0,0,0,,Am venit aici ca să cumpăr o carte despre plante.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:17.62,0:08:23.08,Dialogue,Ryu,0,0,0,,Iar botanistul șef mi-a spus să aflu unde merge Shirayuki astăzi.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:23.94,0:08:26.77,Dialogue,Ryu,0,0,0,,Nu-ți face griji. Nu este treaba mea.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:27.18,0:08:28.73,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Mersi.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:29.29,0:08:31.76,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,Asta e domnița pe care o cunosc.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:31.76,0:08:32.75,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Serios?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:32.75,0:08:37.98,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,Da, doar relaxează-te și comportă-te cum o faci de obicei.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:37.98,0:08:40.15,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Așa voi face. Mersi, Obi.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:41.26,0:08:43.78,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,Missy, I see a certain Master is here.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:43.78,0:08:45.99,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,Privește, acolo sus!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:50.91,0:08:52.76,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Se pare că vă distrați.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:53.24,0:08:54.63,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Nu știam că ar veni și Ryu.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:54.63,0:08:56.95,Dialogue,Ryu,0,0,0,,Eu mă voi întoarce la castel acum.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:56.95,0:08:59.47,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,Am venit până aici doar ca să-i țin companie domniței.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:59.47,0:09:00.10,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,Mă voi întoarce și eu.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:00.58,0:09:01.90,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,Ne vedem la castel!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:01.90,0:09:03.06,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Da, ne vedem acolo!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:07.19,0:09:08.12,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Pornim?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:08.12,0:09:09.15,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Desigur! După tine!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:13.96,0:09:14.85,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Ce ai acolo?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:14.85,0:09:16.36,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Ai cumpărat ceva deja?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:16.70,0:09:18.26,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,E prânzul nostru.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:18.26,0:09:20.86,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Nu am spus că-l voi aduce eu?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:20.86,0:09:22.03,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Oh, așa e.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:22.03,0:09:23.26,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Când ar trebui să-l mâncăm?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:23.26,0:09:26.37,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Haide să ne plimbăm puțin prin oraș, mai întâi.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:27.55,0:09:29.00,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Acest loc chiar e plin de viață.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:29.00,0:09:31.69,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Da. Am mai venit în oraș de multe ori,
Dialogue: 100,0:09:31.69,0:09:34.28,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,dar niciodată să mă plimb sau să fac cumpărături.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:34.28,0:09:36.38,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Pare că te poți pierde cu ușurință aici.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:36.38,0:09:40.89,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Și eu veneam la farmacia de aici destul de des.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:41.62,0:09:43.56,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Ce miros frumos!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:45.06,0:09:47.20,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Arată atât de bine.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:47.20,0:09:50.03,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Poate am putea cumpăra câteva pentru cei de la castel?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:50.03,0:09:52.00,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Un cadou pentru ei, nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:52.00,0:09:57.03,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Mereu mergem împreună, deci nu le-am cumpărat niciodată nimic.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:57.03,0:09:59.99,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Lui Kiki și Mitsuhide le plac dulciurile?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:59.99,0:10:04.24,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Lui Mitsuhide îi place orice e dulce.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:04.24,0:10:08.01,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Dar nu am văzut-o pe Kiki să mănânce dulciuri.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:08.01,0:10:11.17,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Amândoi par atât de diferiți!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:11.54,0:10:15.59,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Da, dar sunt prieteni de atâta timp încât parcă sunt pe aceeași lungime de undă.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:16.30,0:10:20.45,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Încă de la prima lor întâlnire, am fost sigur că vor lucra bine împreună cu mine.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:23.89,0:10:25.84,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Ah, Kiki.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:25.84,0:10:28.34,Dialogue,Kiki,0,0,0,,Bună dimineața, Mitsuhide.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:28.34,0:10:30.70,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Ce? Unde e prințul Zen?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:30.70,0:10:33.30,Dialogue,Kiki,0,0,0,,El este... aici, teoretic.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:36.76,0:10:38.20,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Prințule Zen!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:38.20,0:10:40.36,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Oh, ești doar tu, Mitsuhide.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:40.36,0:10:44.33,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Nu e bine să dormi pe podea, prințule Zen!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:44.70,0:10:48.81,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Ce pot spune? Am fost foarte obosit după ce am terminat cu inspecțiile de ieri.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:48.81,0:10:50.79,Dialogue,Kiki,0,0,0,,Bună dimineața, Maiestate.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:52.01,0:10:54.80,Dialogue,Kiki,0,0,0,,Ar trebui să te trezesc dacă se va mai întâmpla asta în viitor?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:54.80,0:10:57.34,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Ar fi mai bine dacă nu ar trebui s-o faci deloc.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:57.34,0:10:59.26,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Dar dacă se va întâmpla din nou, te rog să-l trezești.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:59.26,0:11:00.89,Dialogue,Kiki,0,0,0,,Am înțeles.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:00.89,0:11:04.72,Dialogue,Kiki,0,0,0,,Maiestate, mi-ar plăcea să confirm planurile pentru azi.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:04.72,0:11:07.29,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,De fapt, vreau să-ți cer ceva, Kiki.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:07.29,0:11:07.85,Dialogue,Kiki,0,0,0,,Ce anume?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:08.22,0:11:13.03,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Nu-mi place să-i tratez pe oamenii din jurul meu ca pe niște servitori.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:13.57,0:11:17.94,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Dacă nu te deranjează, mi-ar plăcea dacă am vorbi informal atunci când suntem doar noi trei.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:19.24,0:11:21.66,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Și, Mitsuhide...
Dialogue: 100,0:11:21.66,0:11:26.66,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,De când a apărut Kiki în peisaj, ai revenit la vechile obiceiuri!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:26.66,0:11:28.19,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Credeam că trecusem peste.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:28.19,0:11:30.04,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Z-Zen...
Dialogue: 100,0:11:30.39,0:11:34.00,Dialogue,Kiki,0,0,0,,Dacă Maiestatea Voastră dorește asta, voi face tot ce-mi stă în putință.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:34.00,0:11:35.84,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Grozav. Spune-mi Zen.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:36.19,0:11:37.46,Dialogue,Kiki,0,0,0,,Bine, Zen.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:38.46,0:11:40.22,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,S-a adaptat foarte repede!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:49.43,0:11:51.23,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Poftim, domnișoară Kiki.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:52.02,0:11:53.14,Dialogue,Kiki,0,0,0,,Mersi.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:54.43,0:11:55.43,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Scuză-mă.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:55.98,0:11:57.72,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Mă întrebam dacă nu ar fi trebuit să fac acel lucru.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:57.72,0:11:58.92,Dialogue,Kiki,0,0,0,,Domnule Mitsuhide.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:59.44,0:12:00.36,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Da?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:00.36,0:12:02.24,Dialogue,Kiki,0,0,0,,E legat de modul de adresare, dar...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:02.24,0:12:04.96,Dialogue,Kiki,0,0,0,,Mi-ai putea spune Kiki?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:05.87,0:12:08.64,Dialogue,Kiki,0,0,0,,Când îmi spui domnișoară Kiki,
Dialogue: 100,0:12:08.64,0:12:11.75,Dialogue,Kiki,0,0,0,,îmi e greu să-i spun Zen Maiestății Sale.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:11.75,0:12:13.41,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Înțeleg.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:13.41,0:12:15.15,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Văd cum te afectează asta.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:15.15,0:12:18.34,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,În acest caz, și tu îmi poți spune Mitsuhide.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:18.34,0:12:20.16,Dialogue,Kiki,0,0,0,,Chiar pot?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:20.16,0:12:22.09,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Da, nu mă deranjează.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:22.09,0:12:24.34,Dialogue,Kiki,0,0,0,,Am înțeles, Mitsuhide.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:25.46,0:12:26.19,Dialogue,Kiki,0,0,0,,Bun.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:27.77,0:12:28.81,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Domnișoară Kiki!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:32.27,0:12:33.27,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Nu...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:35.03,0:12:37.06,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Ki... Kiki.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:44.33,0:12:45.66,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Zen!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:46.49,0:12:48.33,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Se pare că voi doi chiar vă înțelegeți!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:50.29,0:12:53.71,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Nu s-au schimbat deloc de atunci.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:55.08,0:12:56.26,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nici tu nu ai făcut-o.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:57.26,0:13:03.05,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Totuși, sunt sigur că putem vorbi și despre altceva în afară de Mitsuhide când suntem singuri.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:03.05,0:13:04.17,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Bun!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:04.17,0:13:07.13,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Niciun cuvânt despre Mitsuhide începând de acum.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:07.65,0:13:09.28,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Nu până nu ajungem acasă.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:11.11,0:13:12.43,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Ai vrea să ne mai plimbăm puțin?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:13.39,0:13:14.44,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Desigur!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:18.30,0:13:19.44,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,M-am întors!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:19.81,0:13:20.94,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Cum a fost?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:20.94,0:13:23.12,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,Nu ai de ce să-ți faci griji.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:23.12,0:13:26.26,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,M-am asigurat că domnița a ajuns cu bine în oraș.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:26.26,0:13:29.59,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,They're having plenty of fun together right now.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:29.59,0:13:30.41,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Înțeleg.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:30.41,0:13:32.58,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,Din moment ce nu avem zile libere prea des,
Dialogue: 100,0:13:32.58,0:13:36.33,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,nu ar trebui să mergi și tu la o întâlnire cu domnișoara Kiki?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:36.33,0:13:37.98,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,La o întâlnire cu Kiki?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:40.61,0:13:42.68,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,O întâlnire cu Kiki, nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:42.68,0:13:44.44,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Asta ar fi drăguț.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:46.84,0:13:48.01,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,Oh, domnișoară Kiki!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:50.94,0:13:52.13,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,A încuiat ușa!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:52.13,0:13:55.21,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,Am fost închiși aici, Mitsuhide!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:55.21,0:13:58.30,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,{\i1}She doesn't want it {\i0}that{\i1} much?!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:00.47,0:14:01.98,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Unde vrei să mergem acum?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:01.98,0:14:04.69,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Nu voiai să faci niște cumpărături?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:04.69,0:14:07.69,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Așa e! I wanted some stationary for writing letters!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:08.25,0:14:09.49,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Scrisori?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:10.74,0:14:12.74,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,They have so many different ones.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:15.70,0:14:18.12,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,It says that's a fragrant sealing wax!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:18.12,0:14:19.14,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Să vedem.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:21.41,0:14:22.72,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,It's really nice.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:25.29,0:14:26.42,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,It really is!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:27.74,0:14:29.84,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,I'll take it, then.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:29.84,0:14:35.45,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Ar trebui să le scriu oamenilor din Laxdo, cum ar fi, Shuka, și oamenilor din Tanbarun.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:35.45,0:14:36.60,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Ești așa de sârguincioasă.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:36.97,0:14:39.65,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Doar sunt multe persoane pe care nu am timp să merg și să le văd.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:39.65,0:14:42.15,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,De asta ne trimitem scrisori din când în când.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:42.81,0:14:45.07,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Nu cred că se întâmpla asta, dar...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:45.63,0:14:48.45,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Nu primești scrisori de la Raj, nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:49.09,0:14:50.63,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Prințul Raj?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:50.63,0:14:52.91,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Nu, nu, desigur că nu!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:55.48,0:14:57.34,Dialogue,Raj,0,0,0,,C-Ce e asta?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:57.34,0:14:59.92,Dialogue,Sakaki,0,0,0,,O prăjitură, plină ochi cu mere, prințul meu.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:59.92,0:15:01.54,Dialogue,Raj,0,0,0,,Pot să văd și eu asta!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:01.54,0:15:03.64,Dialogue,Raj,0,0,0,,Dar ce vrea să însemne asta, Sakaki?!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:03.64,0:15:06.40,Dialogue,Raj,0,0,0,,Ți-am spus să nu-mi mai aduci mere!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:06.40,0:15:09.80,Dialogue,Sakaki,0,0,0,,Perhaps the kitchen staff\N had an abundance of apples.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:09.80,0:15:11.93,Dialogue,Sakaki,0,0,0,,I promise it wasn't meant to be malicious.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:12.61,0:15:15.10,Dialogue,Sakaki,0,0,0,,Please, have some more apple tea.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:15.10,0:15:17.35,Dialogue,Raj,0,0,0,,{\i1}Apples remind me of her too much.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:17.35,0:15:18.85,Dialogue,Raj,0,0,0,,{\i1}The apple-haired girl.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:21.90,0:15:25.52,Dialogue,Sakaki,0,0,0,,Actually, it's been a while since \Nthe last time you held a ball.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:26.15,0:15:28.37,Dialogue,Sakaki,0,0,0,,Has something changed?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:28.37,0:15:30.67,Dialogue,Raj,0,0,0,,It's not because of any particular reason.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:30.67,0:15:32.24,Dialogue,Raj,0,0,0,,They bore me is all.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:32.24,0:15:33.80,Dialogue,Sakaki,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:34.77,0:15:36.81,Dialogue,Sakaki,0,0,0,,{\i1}Boredom makes me remember...
Dialogue: 100,0:15:36.81,0:15:37.62,Dialogue,Sakaki,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur0\1a&HFF&\t(709,1418,\blur25\shad0\bord0)}Those times.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:37.62,0:15:38.25,Dialogue,Sakaki,0,0,0,,{\b1\i1\blur12\shad0\bord0\c&H000000&\t(120,0,\blur30)}Those times.
Dialogue: 101,0:15:36.81,0:15:38.25,Dialogue,Sakaki,0,0,0,,{\i1\blur0\t(709,1418,\blur25)\bord0\shad0}Those times.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:40.09,0:15:41.73,Dialogue,Raj,0,0,0,,I'm not doing this anymore!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:41.73,0:15:43.54,Dialogue,Raj,0,0,0,,It's a waste of time! That's boring!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:43.54,0:15:45.60,Dialogue,Sakaki,0,0,0,,Crying over some blisters...
Dialogue: 100,0:15:45.60,0:15:48.01,Dialogue,Sakaki,0,0,0,,We haven't even been doing this for three days.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:48.01,0:15:50.88,Dialogue,Raj,0,0,0,,Won't it be fine if you just protect me yourself?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:53.75,0:15:58.85,Dialogue,Sakaki,0,0,0,,Prince Raj, who was raised as the \Nspoiled first prince of his kingdom,
Dialogue: 100,0:15:58.85,0:16:03.41,Dialogue,Sakaki,0,0,0,,already had it in his mind that he'd \Nget everything he wanted from me.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:04.48,0:16:06.59,Dialogue,Sakaki,0,0,0,,Prince Raj, it's time for your politics studies.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:06.59,0:16:08.03,Dialogue,Raj,0,0,0,,My stomach hurts!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:08.71,0:16:11.02,Dialogue,Sakaki,0,0,0,,Prince Raj, it's time for your horse riding lessons.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:11.02,0:16:13.53,Dialogue,Raj,0,0,0,,I don't need more lessons!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:14.55,0:16:17.77,Dialogue,Sakaki,0,0,0,,Whatever he did, he'd grow bored quickly,
Dialogue: 100,0:16:17.77,0:16:19.87,Dialogue,Sakaki,0,0,0,,and yet, there was one thing he enjoyed.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:21.37,0:16:23.93,Dialogue,Sakaki,0,0,0,,Prince Raj excelled in the fine arts.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:25.00,0:16:29.18,Dialogue,Sakaki,0,0,0,,He found a home in poetry where \Nhe could express himself gracefully.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:30.86,0:16:33.26,Dialogue,Sakaki,0,0,0,,This makes me remember the old days, Prince Raj.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:33.63,0:16:34.48,Dialogue,Raj,0,0,0,,What makes you?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:34.48,0:16:36.06,Dialogue,Sakaki,0,0,0,,Ah, nothing.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:36.06,0:16:39.24,Dialogue,Sakaki,0,0,0,,I was just remembering you used to be\N quite skilled at composing poems.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:39.24,0:16:43.73,Dialogue,Sakaki,0,0,0,,How about sending Miss Shirayuki\N a poem about her?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:44.05,0:16:46.23,Dialogue,Raj,0,0,0,,A poem about Miss Shirayuki?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:52.85,0:16:56.85,Dialogue,Raj,0,0,0,,R-Red... red flower you are,
Dialogue: 100,0:16:56.85,0:16:58.49,Dialogue,Raj,0,0,0,,but a flower with thorns you are.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:58.49,0:16:59.84,Dialogue,Sakaki,0,0,0,,You've lost your skill, I suppose.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:01.26,0:17:03.71,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Did you bake this, Shirayuki?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:03.71,0:17:04.96,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:04.96,0:17:09.13,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Kiki told me you like pies, \Nso I thought I'd make one for you.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:09.13,0:17:10.46,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Here, take a piece.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:13.26,0:17:14.17,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,It's great!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:14.50,0:17:15.86,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:18.42,0:17:21.74,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Shirayuki, did you see something \Ntoday that you wanted?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:22.77,0:17:24.56,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,I'd like to buy it for you.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:25.59,0:17:27.56,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,F-For me?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:27.56,0:17:28.25,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:28.25,0:17:29.48,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,You don't have to!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:30.48,0:17:32.40,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Then it's decided. I'll give you a memento.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:34.40,0:17:35.68,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Something to remember today by.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:35.68,0:17:36.62,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:36.62,0:17:37.46,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,A dress?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:37.46,0:17:40.60,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,I-I don't really know much about dresses...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:43.71,0:17:46.11,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,They apparently have a lot of things here.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:46.11,0:17:47.85,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Pens, ornaments, and so on.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:47.85,0:17:48.89,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,They really do.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:48.89,0:17:50.29,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,So many things here!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:51.49,0:17:52.53,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Shirayuki!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:57.30,0:17:58.85,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Bookmarks!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:58.85,0:18:00.38,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,So pretty...
Dialogue: 100,0:18:06.68,0:18:08.50,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Do you like this one?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:08.50,0:18:10.01,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:14.65,0:18:17.32,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:18.23,0:18:20.07,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Thank you, Zen.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:34.14,0:18:37.94,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,I heard once that you're supposed \Nto do this on such a lovely day.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:37.94,0:18:39.40,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Who said that?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:39.40,0:18:41.26,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Who was it, I wonder...
Dialogue: 100,0:18:41.26,0:18:43.78,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,I feel like his name started with M.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:45.15,0:18:48.49,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,{\i1}We took each other's hand and began our story.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:49.55,0:18:53.86,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hope the sound of its pages being turned
Dialogue: 100,0:18:53.86,0:18:57.06,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,{\i1}will, like our footsteps, echo in unison
Dialogue: 100,0:18:57.06,0:18:58.60,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,{\i1}as we continue walking together.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:20.15,0:19:22.18,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,We've walked so much!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:22.18,0:19:24.63,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Do your feet hurt?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:24.63,0:19:26.68,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:27.52,0:19:31.23,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Zen, is there anything else you wanted to look at?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:31.23,0:19:32.38,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:32.38,0:19:33.43,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:33.43,0:19:36.69,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Like your own souvenir or memento.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:37.07,0:19:40.90,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,If there's anything {\i1}you{\i0} want, I want to know that.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:42.00,0:19:43.07,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Is this for a gift to me?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:43.39,0:19:44.36,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:01.78,0:20:04.64,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,I'm not sure. I...
Dialogue: 100,0:20:20.87,0:20:23.53,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Shirayuki, did you have fun today?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:24.79,0:20:25.97,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,So much fun!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:27.20,0:20:30.63,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Those words are the greatest present for me.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:39.84,0:20:40.95,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Mitsuhide!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:41.45,0:20:42.35,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Kiki!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:43.26,0:20:44.71,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Obi.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:44.71,0:20:46.17,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Don't sleep in a place like that.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:47.68,0:20:49.35,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,You're giving these to us?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:49.35,0:20:50.34,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Are these presents?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:50.34,0:20:52.43,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Yeah, and I'm going to sleep now.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:53.64,0:20:55.56,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,I'll be counting on you tomorrow again.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:09.33,0:21:11.20,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,Is that for me?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:11.53,0:21:12.90,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,When did you write it?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:13.49,0:21:16.24,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,While you were getting the bookmark wrapped,
Dialogue: 100,0:21:16.24,0:21:18.46,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,I found somewhere to write a letter.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:19.11,0:21:23.46,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,A letter with only two lines.\N Just what I'd expect from Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:26.02,0:21:27.34,Dialogue,Zen,0,0,0,,It has a really nice fragrance.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:28.80,0:21:29.97,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dear Zen,
Dialogue: 100,0:21:30.60,0:21:33.81,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm happy we got to walk around town together.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:34.42,0:21:37.89,Dialogue,Red,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you for today.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:41.56,0:21:42.78,Dialogue,Kiki,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:42.78,0:21:45.61,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,An ink bottle that glows at night, apparently.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:45.97,0:21:48.49,Dialogue,Kiki,0,0,0,,Mine appears to be a brooch with a dog on it.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:48.49,0:21:49.54,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,That's a cat.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:49.54,0:21:52.05,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,No, that's obviously a lion.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:52.05,0:21:53.20,Dialogue,Kiki,0,0,0,,What did you get?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:53.20,0:21:56.96,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,An antique ornamental cork for liquor bottles, apparently.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:59.41,0:22:03.91,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,I suppose it {\i1}is{\i0} the first time Zen's \Nbought presents for anyone, isn't it?
Dialogue: 100,0:22:03.91,0:22:07.14,Dialogue,Kiki,0,0,0,,I just want to know if he put \Nany thought into these gifts.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:07.14,0:22:09.76,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,I really wonder where I should put mine.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:09.76,0:22:11.97,Dialogue,Kiki,0,0,0,,How about hanging it on your neck like a pendant?
Dialogue: 100,0:22:11.97,0:22:12.70,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,Lame...
Dialogue: 100,0:22:12.70,0:22:13.65,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Nu spune asta!
Dialogue: 100,0:22:13.65,0:22:15.00,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Don't finish that thought!
Dialogue: 100,0:22:15.00,0:22:16.38,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,I'll definitely use mine!
Dialogue: 100,0:22:16.38,0:22:19.43,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,It's cool how it shines at night!
Dialogue: 100,0:22:19.43,0:22:20.53,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Privește!
Dialogue: 100,0:22:20.53,0:22:22.54,Dialogue,Mitsu,0,0,0,,Strălucește precum un curcubeu!
Dialogue: 100,0:22:22.54,0:22:23.29,Dialogue,Kiki,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:23.29,0:22:24.67,Dialogue,Obi,0,0,0,,Dazzling.
